This paper deals with wireless communication networks and resource allocation, which are topics commonly found in the Information Theory (cs.IT) and Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also considers optimization problems and joint optimization of multiple parameters, which are relevant to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses beamforming, which is a topic in Multimedia (cs.MM) and Communications and Networking (cs.CE) sub-categories. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IT and cs.NI, followed by cs.SY, cs.MM, and cs.CE.
